sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User as Utilisateur
    participant Browser as Navigateur
    participant BFF as BFF Next (webapp/admin)
    participant Keycloak as Keycloak
    participant ApiTs as app-api-ts
    participant Pg as PostgreSQL

    Browser->>BFF: GET/POST /api/v1/*
    BFF->>BFF: verifier Origin / Sec-Fetch-Site
    BFF->>BFF: resoudre session serveur
    alt session absente ou expiree
        BFF->>Keycloak: refresh / verif OIDC
        Keycloak-->>BFF: token / echec auth
    end
    BFF->>ApiTs: requete upstream avec Authorization Bearer
    BFF->>ApiTs: X-Request-ID + traceparent + tracestate
    ApiTs->>ApiTs: verifier JWT / role / permissions
    ApiTs->>Pg: lecture ou ecriture SQL
    Pg-->>ApiTs: rows / ack
    ApiTs-->>BFF: JSON normalise
    BFF-->>Browser: reponse same-origin no-store
